state.unicode: You do not control the Magical Forest associated with this Heathland region.
This is a pacified Heathland (owned by yourself, an ally, or is razed). The nearby Magical Forest will heal more quickly as a result.
This is a hostile Heathland. It will drain the health of the nearby Magical Forest while occupied by an enemy. Work towards peace with its owner or drive them out!
This is a Magical Forest. Pacify its bordering Heathlands to strengthen its connection to the Worldroots and increase its health.
This is a neutral Heathland. It has no effect on the health of the nearby Magical Forest. Occupy or raze it, or ally with its owner, and it will begin to provide benefits.
